          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "aspnet_PersonalizationPerUser_GetPageSettings",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve personalization settings for a specific user and page within an application. It involves identifying the application, path, and user, updating the user's last activity date, and then fetching the page settings associated with the user and path."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
