      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves multiple steps, including fetching identifiers, updating records, and retrieving data. It uses conditional logic to handle cases where identifiers are not found, which adds to its complexity. However, it does not involve complex joins or transactions, keeping it at a medium complexity level."
        }
      ]
    },
